CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 11, 1954, p. 13, reads: "TURKEY 'N' EVERYTHING - Members of the Gaydettes Club of East Liberty are pleased because they were able to give away three baskets of food Thanksgiving.  One of the baskets contained a seven-pound turkey.  The nine members are Jeannette McElroy, Rita Cannady, Virginia Haley, Patricia McGuire, Lois Jenkins, Janey Banks, Floretta Byrd, Delores Johnson and Barbara Ann Goins. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of nine women of the Gaydettes Club, including front row: Janice McElroy, Delores Johnson, Barbara Goins, Floretta Byrd Irvin, second row: Rita Johnson wearing light colored blouse with dark trim, Virginia Haley, Pat McGuire, Lois Jenkins, and Janice Banks wearing dark scarf under collar, gathered around basket with food including turkey, in domestic interior for Thanksgiving food drive
